snippet.title: Reaktor - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to your steam wishlist! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2950640/Reaktor/

Create massive chain reactions by launching tetrominoes at a spinning nuclear core. Keep it casual or cause a meltdown. Play solo or go nuclear with up to four players.
